query: WITH entities AS (SELECT status, last_activity, id FROM core_customers WHERE ((status = $1) AND ((last_activity IS NOT DISTINCT FROM $4) AND COALESCE(id < $3, true) OR COALESCE(last_activity < $4, last_activity IS NOT NULL))) ORDER BY last_activity DESC NULLS LAST, id DESC LIMIT $2) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: CustomerId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN core_customer_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.last_activity desc nulls last, i.id desc, i.id, e.sequence
